overview.en: DISN is a digital currency jointly issued by the research and development team of Dragons' memory blockchain technology, aiming to enhance transaction convenience, asset liquidity, and digital experience in the fields of memory blockchain+gaming, tourism, NFT, social networking, etc. The project has received participation from several well-known figures in the industry, including experts such as Haseeb Qureshi and Eva Kaili. DISN provides users with more convenient trading methods and promotes innovative development in fields such as gaming, tourism, NFT, etc.
overview.zh: DISN是由Dragons區塊鏈技術研發團隊聯合發行的數字貨幣，旨在解決區塊鏈+遊戲、文旅、NFT、社交等領域的交易便捷性、資產流動性以及數位化體驗的增強。該專案得到了多位行業內知名人士的參與，包括Haseeb Qureshi和Eva Kaili等專家。DISN為用戶提供更便捷的交易方式，並推動遊戲、文旅、NFT等領域的創新發展。
